'''第80届奥斯卡颁奖典礼'''是[[美国电影艺术与科学学院|美国电影艺术与科学学院]]旨在奖励[[2007年电影|2007年最优秀电影]]的一场晚会，于[[太平洋时区|太平洋时区]]2008年2月24日下午17点30分（[[北美东部时区|北美东部时区]]晚上20点30分）在[[美国|美国]][[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]][[好莱坞|好莱坞]]的[[杜比剧院|杜比剧院]]举行，共计颁发24个类别的[[奥斯卡金像奖|奥斯卡金像奖]]（也称[[学院奖|学院奖]]）。晚会通过[[美国广播公司|美国广播公司]]在[[美国电视|美国]]直播，由吉尔·凯茨（{{lang|en|Gil Cates}}）担任制片人，路易斯·{{lang|en|J}}·霍维茨（{{lang|en|Louis J, Horvitz}}）导演<ref name="Gil Cates">{{cite news|newspaper=[[芝加哥太阳报|Chicago Sun-Times]] |url=http://blogs.suntimes.com/awards/2007/09/cates_tapped_for_record_14th_o.html |title=Cates tapped for record 14th Oscars telecast |last=O'Connor |first=Thomas |publisher=Sun Times Media Group |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714213035/http://blogs.suntimes.com/awards/2007/09/cates_tapped_for_record_14th_o.html |date=2007-09-12 |accessdate=2016-01-27 |archivedate=2014-07-14 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Kivel | first = Matthew | title = Oscar director back a 12th time | accessdate = 2016-01-27 | work = Variety | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151222085444/http://variety.com/2007/film/news/oscar-director-back-a-12th-time-1117978000/ | url = http://variety.com/2007/film/news/oscar-director-back-a-12th-time-1117978000/ | publisher = Penske Media Corporation | date = 2007-12-19 | archivedate = 2015-12-22}}</ref>，曾于两年前主持[[第78届奥斯卡金像奖|第78届颁奖晚会]]的笑匠兼[[談話節目|脱口秀]]主持[[乔恩·斯图尔特|乔恩·斯图尔特]]第2次担任主持人<ref name="Jon Stewart host">{{cite news | title = Academy to Invite Jon Stewart Back as Oscar Host | last = Cieply | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2007/09/12/movies/awardsseason/12stewart.html?_r=1 | first = Michael | publisher = Arthur Ochs Sulzberger, Jr. | newspaper = [[纽约时报|The New York Times]] | date = 2007-09-12 | accessdate = 2016-01-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150605044741/http://www.nytimes.com/2007/09/12/movies/awardsseason/12stewart.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-06-05}}</ref>。两周前的2月9日，女演员[[杰西卡·阿尔芭|杰西卡·阿尔芭]]在加利福尼亚州[[比佛利山_(加利福尼亚州)|比佛利山]]的[[比佛利威尔希尔饭店|比佛利威尔希尔饭店]]主持颁发了[[奥斯卡科技成果奖|奥斯卡科技成果奖]]<ref>{{cite news | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/tech/news/techinnovations/2008-02-11-alba-tech-oscars_N.htm | title = Alba dazzles nerds at tech Oscars | accessdate = 2016-01-27 | date = 2008-02-11 | work = USA Today | publisher = Gannett Company | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121024232749/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/tech/news/techinnovations/2008-02-11-alba-tech-oscars_N.htm | last = Pearson | first = Ryan | archivedate = 2012-10-24 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

《[[老无所依|老无所依]]》获得包括[[奥斯卡最佳影片奖|最佳影片]]在内的4项大奖，是这个夜晚的最大赢家<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Halbfinger | first1 = David | last2 = Cieply | first2 = Michael | title = ‘No Country for Old Men’ Wins Oscar Tug of War | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2008/02/25/movies/awardsseason/25osca.html?pagewanted=all | accessdate = 2016-01-27 | newspaper = The New York Times | publisher = Arthur Ochs Sulzberger, Jr. | date = 2008-02-25 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090424210130/http://www.nytimes.com/2008/02/25/movies/awardsseason/25osca.html?pagewanted=all | archivedate = 2009-04-24}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Burr | first = Ty | title = Foreign accents Cotillard, Swinton, Bardem take top awards in a surprising night in Hollywood | newspaper = The Boston Globe | publisher = John W. Henry | date = 2008-02-25}}</ref>。其它获奖作品包括胜出3项的《[[谍影重重3|谍影重重3]]》、获奖2项的《[[玫瑰人生_(電影)|玫瑰人生]]》和《[[血色将至|血色将至]]》，以及胜出1项的《[[贖罪_(電影)|赎罪]]》、《[[伪钞制造者|伪钞制造者]]》、《[[伊莉莎白：輝煌年代|伊莉莎白：輝煌年代]]》、《[[保险被拒|保险被拒]]》（{{lang|en|''Freeheld''}}）、《[[魔幻羅盤|魔幻羅盤]]》、《[[朱诺_(电影)|朱诺]]》、《[[敵對同謀|敵對同謀]]》、《[[扒手莫扎特|扒手莫扎特]]》（{{lang|en|''The Mozart of Pickpockets''}}）、《[[曾經。愛是唯一|曾經。愛是唯一]]》、《[[彼得与狼_(动画短片)|彼得与狼]]》（{{lang|en|''Peter and the Wolf''}}）、《[[美食总动员|美食总动员]]》、《[[魔街理髮師_(2007年電影)|理发师陶德]]》和《[[开往暗处的的士|开往暗处的的士]]》（{{lang|en|''Taxi to the Dark Side''}}）。晚会的电视直播平均吸引了约3,200万美国观众收看，是电视观众人数最少的一届<ref name="Finke">{{cite news | last = Finke | first = Nikki | title = Update: Wow, Worst-Rated Oscars Since Nielsen Started Tracking Them in 1974! | accessdate = 2016-01-28 | publisher = Penske Media Corporation | date = 2008-02-25 | url = http://deadline.com/2008/02/update-worst-rated-oscars-since-nielsens-started-tracking-them-in-1974-4977/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160127162926/http://deadline.com/2008/02/update-worst-rated-oscars-since-nielsens-started-tracking-them-in-1974-4977/ | archivedate = 2016-01-27 | deadurl = no | work = Deadline.com}}</ref>。

== 获奖和提名 ==
2008年1月22日，[[美国电影艺术与科学学院|美国电影艺术与科学学院]]主席希德·甘尼斯（{{lang|en|Sid Ganis}}）和女演员[[凯西·贝茨|凯西·贝茨]]一起在[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[比佛利山_(加利福尼亚州)|比佛利山]]的[[塞缪尔·戈尔德温剧院|塞缪尔·戈尔德温剧院]]公布第80届奥斯卡金像奖提名名单<ref>{{cite news | last = Gray | first = Tim | title = Oscar nominations announced | archivedate = 2015-12-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151223094924/http://variety.com/2008/film/news/oscar-nominations-announced-1117979394/ | url = http://variety.com/2008/film/news/oscar-nominations-announced-1117979394/ | accessdate = 2016-01-28 | work = Variety | publisher = Penske Media Corporation | date = 2008-01-22 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。《[[老无所依|老无所依]]》和《[[血色将至|血色将至]]》均以8项提名领跑<ref>{{cite news|last=Barnes |first=Brooks |title=‘No Country’ and ‘There Will Be Blood’ Lead Oscars |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/01/23/movies/awardsseason/23oscarscnd.html |accessdate=2016-01-27 |newspaper=The New York Times |publisher=Arthur Ochs Sulzberger, Jr. |date=2008-01-23 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20160127163648/http://www.nytimes.com/2008/01/23/movies/awardsseason/23oscarscnd.html?_r=0 |archivedate=2016-01-27 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

获奖名单在2008年2月24日举行的颁奖典礼上公布<ref>{{cite news | last = Kennedy | first = Lisa | title = Having no dominant film seems fair | url = http://www.denverpost.com/familynews/ci_8355520?source=pkg | accessdate = 2016-01-28 | work = The Denver Post | publisher = Mac Tully | date = 2008-02-25 | archivedate = 2016-01-28 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160128054243/http://www.denverpost.com/familynews/ci_8355520?source=pkg}}</ref>。[[科恩兄弟|伊森·科恩和乔尔·科恩]]一起获[[奥斯卡最佳导演奖|导演奖]]，是历史上第二次有两位导演因同一部电影获奖，上次出现这种情况是1961年的电影《[[西城故事_(1961年電影)|西区故事]]》，[[杰罗姆·罗宾斯|杰罗姆·罗宾斯]]和[[罗伯特·怀斯|罗伯特·怀斯]]共同获奖<ref>{{cite news | last = Coyle | first = Jake | title = Oscars Honor Coens As Best Director(s) | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121108051430/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/2008-02-25-2405067657_x.htm | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/2008-02-25-2405067657_x.htm | accessdate = 2016-01-28 | work = USA Today | publisher = Gannett Company | date = 2008-02-25 | archivedate = 2012-11-08}}</ref>。获表演类奖项肯定的4名演员都不是在美国出生，这种情况此前还只出现过1次<ref>{{cite news | last = O'Neil | first = Tom | title = Oscar invasion! | url = http://goldderby.latimes.com/awards_goldderby/2008/02/oscar-invasion.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151222201754/http://goldderby.latimes.com/awards_goldderby/2008/02/oscar-invasion.html | accessdate = 2016-01-28 | work = Los Angeles Times | publisher = Austin Beutner | date = 2008-02-24 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-12-22}}</ref>。[[丹尼尔·戴-刘易斯|丹尼尔·戴-刘易斯]]成为历史上第8位两次获[[奥斯卡最佳男主角奖|男主角奖]]的演员<ref>{{cite news | last = O'Neil | first1 = Tom | title = Day-Lewis is 8th double Oscar lead actor | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151118201222/http://goldderby.latimes.com/awards_goldderby/2008/02/day-lewis-is-8t.html | url = http://goldderby.latimes.com/awards_goldderby/2008/02/day-lewis-is-8t.html | accessdate = 2016-01-28 | work = Los Angeles Times | publisher = Austin Beutner | date = 2008-02-24 | archivedate = 2015-11-18}}</ref>。女主角奖得主[[玛丽昂·歌迪亚|玛丽昂·歌迪亚]]是主演1961年电影《[[烽火母女泪|烽火母女泪]]》（{{lang|it|La ciociara}}）的[[索菲娅·罗兰|索菲娅·罗兰]]之后首位以非英语电影获女主角奖的演员，也是历史上第5位[[在电影中未说英语而获奥斯卡金像奖提名的演员列表|在电影中未说英语而获奖的演员]]<ref>{{cite news | last = Gallo | first = Phil | title = ‘No Country’ big winner at Oscars | url = http://variety.com/2008/film/news/no-country-big-winner-at-oscars-1117981391/ | accessdate = 2016-01-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151222205111/http://variety.com/2008/film/news/no-country-big-winner-at-oscars-1117981391/ | work = Variety | publisher = Penske Media Corporation | date = 2008-02-24 | archivedate = 2015-12-22 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。获女配角奖的[[凯特·布兰切特|凯特·布兰切特]]则成为历史上第11位[[一年获两项奥斯卡金像奖提名演员列表|同年获两项表演类奖项提名的演员]]<ref name="EW">{{cite news | last = Karger | first = Dave | title = The unpredictable 2008 Oscars | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151122194115/http://www.ew.com/article/2008/01/25/unpredictable-2008-oscars | deadurl = no | url = http://www.ew.com/article/2008/01/25/unpredictable-2008-oscars | accessdate = 2016-01-28 | work = Entertainment Weekly | publisher = Time Inc. | date = 2008-01-25 | archivedate = 2015-11-22}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|publisher=Postmedia Network |title=A little help from his friends |work=National Post |accessdate=2016-01-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160127071440/http://www.nationalpost.com/opinion/columnists/story.html?id=26713113-e72b-4e54-b272-d60ee0b72e75&p=1 |archivedate=2016-01-27 |url=http://www.nationalpost.com/opinion/columnists/story.html?id=26713113-e72b-4e54-b272-d60ee0b72e75&p=1 }}</ref>。布兰切特曾因在1998年电影《[[伊莉莎白_(電影)|伊丽莎白]]》中扮演英国女王[[伊丽莎白一世_(英格兰)|伊丽莎白一世]]获女主角奖提名，这次又因在《[[伊丽莎白2：黄金时代|伊丽莎白2：黄金时代]]》中饰演同一角色获同一奖项提名，成为历史上首位扮演同一人物而两度获提名的女演员，也是第5位达成这一目标的演员<ref>{{cite news | last = O'Neill | first = Tom | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151222204108/http://goldderby.latimes.com/awards_goldderby/2008/01/blanchett-sets.html | title = Blanchett sets another first | url = http://goldderby.latimes.com/awards_goldderby/2008/01/blanchett-sets.html | accessdate = 2016-01-28 | work = Los Angeles Times | publisher = Tribune Company | date = 2008-01-22 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-12-22}}</ref>。获[[奥斯卡最佳男配角奖|男配角奖]]提名的[[哈尔·霍尔布鲁克|哈尔·霍尔布鲁克]]已有82岁，刷新表演类奖项最年长男性提名人的纪录<ref>{{cite news | title = Academy Award Nominee Hal Holbrook | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160128101749/http://www.today.com/allday/academy-award-nominee-hal-holbrook-1C9385251 | url = http://www.today.com/allday/academy-award-nominee-hal-holbrook-1C9385251 | accessdate = 2016-01-28 | publisher = NBCUniversal | work = NBC News | date = 2008-01-22 | archivedate = 2016-01-28 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。此外，获[[奥斯卡荣誉奖|荣誉奖]]的[[罗伯特·波义耳_(艺术指导设计师)|罗伯特·波义耳]]（{{lang|en|Robert F. Boyle}}）已是98岁高龄，创下最年长获奖人的新纪录<ref>{{cite news | title = 45 Fun Facts About the Oscars | url = http://parade.com/130996/parade/oscar-fun-facts/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151225171248/http://parade.com/130996/parade/oscar-fun-facts/ | accessdate = 2016-01-28 | work = Parade | publisher = Condé Nast | date = 2012-02-26 | archivedate = 2015-12-25 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

