== 典礼资讯 ==
[[File:Jon_Stewart_at_Cabaret_2008_benefit.jpg|thumb]]是第80届奥斯卡颁奖典礼的主持人]]
2007年9月，美国电影艺术与科学学院决定聘请吉尔·凯茨（{{lang|en|Gil Cates}}）负责第80届奥斯卡颁奖典礼的制作，这也成为他第14次担任制作人，创下新的纪录<ref name="THR">{{cite news | title = Cates to produce Academy Awards | url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/cates-produce-academy-awards-149925 | accessdate = 2016-01-29 | work = [[好莱坞报道|The Hollywood Reporter]] | publisher = Prometheus Global Media | date = 2007-09-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151223180310/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/cates-produce-academy-awards-149925 | archivedate = 2015-12-23 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。甘尼斯对此表示，凯茨“才华横溢……创意十足，而且对奥斯卡抱有极大热忱。所有这些特点结合起来，让这个夜晚变得让人无比期待”<ref name="THR" />。凯茨获聘后立即选择男演员、笑匠兼[[谈话节目|谈话节目]]主持人[[乔恩·斯图尔特|乔恩·斯图尔特]]担任2008年颁奖晚会司仪，称“乔恩在[[第78届奥斯卡金像奖|第78届颁奖典礼]]上的主持非常出彩……他既聪明、反应又快，会搞笑而且热爱电影，人也没说的。我们还能有什么不满意的呢？”<ref>{{cite news | last = Piccalo | first = Gina | title = Jon Stewart gets an Oscar sequel | url = http://articles.latimes.com/2007/sep/13/news/wk-stewart13 | accessdate = 2016-01-29 | work = Los Angeles Times | publisher = Austin Beutner | date = 2007-09-13 | archivedate = 2015-12-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151223141249/http://articles.latimes.com/2007/sep/13/news/wk-stewart13 | deadurl = no}}</ref>

[[2007年－2008年美国编剧协会大罢工|2007年－2008年美国编剧协会大罢工]]对颁奖典礼的电视转播及周边活动构成影响<ref>{{cite news | last = Cohen | first = Sandy | title = Awards shows could suffer in WGA strike | work = USA Today | publisher = Gannett Company | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/2007-11-14-award-shows-strike_N.htm | accessdate = 2016-01-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151223091339/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/2007-11-14-award-shows-strike_N.htm | archivedate = 2015-12-23 | date = 2007-11-14 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。这场劳资纠纷开始1个多月后，正在罢工的[[美国编剧协会|美国编剧协会]]拒绝接受艺术与科学学院的请求，以致过往颁奖典礼的视频剪辑片段在2008年晚会上播放的方式受限<ref>{{cite news | last = McNairy | first = Dave | title = WGA rejects waiver requests | url = http://variety.com/2007/film/news/wga-rejects-waiver-requests-1117977878/ | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151223094105/http://variety.com/2007/film/news/wga-rejects-waiver-requests-1117977878/ | work = Variety | publisher = Penske Media Corporation | date = 2007-12-17 | archivedate = 2015-12-23 | accessdate = 2016-01-29}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Finke | first = Nikki | title = No WGA Waivers For Globes Or Oscars (And Other News From Tonight’s Meeting); AMPTP Nominates WGA For "Worst Union" | work = Deadline.com | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160123042117/http://deadline.com/2007/12/no-wga-waivers-for-golden-globes-oscars-4454/ | url = http://deadline.com/2007/12/no-wga-waivers-for-golden-globes-oscars-4454/ | accessdate = 2016-01-29 | publisher = Penske Media Corporation | date = 2007-12-17 | archivedate = 2016-01-23}}</ref>。1988年的[[第60届奥斯卡金像奖|第60届奥斯卡颁奖典礼]]是在[[1988年美国编剧协会大罢工|这年编剧罢工]]开始37天后举行，当时主办方已有准备，所需素材都已完成制作，所有演员都应邀出席<ref>{{cite news | last = Killday | title = Oscar has experience with strike-related uncertainty | url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscar-has-experience-strike-related-104329 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151125065308/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscar-has-experience-strike-related-104329 | accessdate = 2016-01-29 | work = The Hollywood Reporter | publisher = Prometheus Global Media | date = 2008-02-08 | archivedate = 2015-11-25 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Cieply | first = Michael | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151117015002/http://articles.latimes.com/1988-04-12/news/mn-783_1_picture-winner | url = http://articles.latimes.com/1988-04-12/news/mn-783_1_picture-winner | title = 'Last Emperor' Reigns Over Oscar Ceremonies : Best Picture Winner Adds Eight Other Awards; Cher and Douglas Take Top Prizes for Acting | work = Los Angeles Times | publisher = Austin Beutner | date = 1988-04-12 | accessdate = 2016-01-29 | archivedate = 2015-11-17}}</ref>。

学院起初预计罢工会持续到晚会当晚，所以制订有备用方案，不包含演员上台领奖的环节<ref>{{cite news | last = Gensler | first = Howard | title = Plan B being developed for Oscar night | accessdate = 2016-01-29 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151223142251/http://articles.philly.com/2008-01-31/entertainment/25253613_1_oscars-leslie-unger-sid-ganis | work = The Philadelphia Inquirer | date = 2008-01-31 | archivedate = 2015-12-23 | publisher = Philadelphia Media Network | url = http://articles.philly.com/2008-01-31/entertainment/25253613_1_oscars-leslie-unger-sid-ganis}}</ref>。其中虽然还是会有歌舞曲目表演，但更多镜头还是聚焦在历史性的视频片段上，以期强调奥斯卡金像奖80周年<ref>{{cite news | last = Bierly | first = Mandi | title = Oscars to go on, possibly with 'packages of film and concepts | work = Entertainment Weekly | publisher = Time Warner | date = 2008-02-24 | accessdate = 2016-01-29 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150927145646/http://www.ew.com/article/2008/01/31/oscars-jon-stew | archivedate = 2015-09-27 | url = http://www.ew.com/article/2008/01/31/oscars-jon-stew}}</ref>。不过，事实证明这一计划并不必要，美国编剧协会同电影和电视制片人同盟达成协议，罢工于2008年2月12日结束，因此颁奖典礼直接按原订方案举行<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Horn | first1 = John | last2 = Piccalo | first2 = Gina | title = Oscars just glad to be scrambling | url = http://articles.latimes.com/2008/feb/12/entertainment/et-oscars12 | accessdate = 2016-01-29 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151223142533/http://articles.latimes.com/2008/feb/12/entertainment/et-oscars12 | work = Los Angeles Times | publisher = Austin Beutner | date = 2008-02-12 | archivedate = 2015-12-23}}</ref>。

=== 提名电影票房表现 ===
与之前几年类似，本届奥斯卡金像奖角逐中小成本独立制作要比票房大片更受表睐<ref>{{cite news | last = Goldstein | first = Patrick | title = Once again, the indies will rule | accessdate = 2016-01-29 | work = Los Angeles Times | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151223142625/http://articles.latimes.com/2008/jan/23/entertainment/et-oscargoldstein23 | url = http://articles.latimes.com/2008/jan/23/entertainment/et-oscargoldstein23 | publisher = Austin Beutner | date = 2008-01-23 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-12-23}}</ref><ref name="NYT Oscars">{{cite news | last = Carr | first = David | title = In Oscars, No Country for Hit Films | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2008/03/03/business/media/03carr.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081210015736/http://www.nytimes.com/2008/03/03/business/media/03carr.html | accessdate = 2016-01-27 | work = The New York Times | publisher = Arthur Ochs Sulzberger, Jr. | date = 2008-03-03 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2008-12-10}}</ref>。截至2008年1月22日提名公布时，全部5部获最佳影片奖提名的电影在美国的[[票房|票房]]总收入为2亿1674万1290美元，平均每部4334万8258美元<ref name="BoxOfficeMojoOscars">{{cite news | archivedate = 2016-01-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160120210009/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/oscar/chart/?yr=2007&p=.htm | deadurl = no | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/oscar/chart/?yr=2007&p=.htm | title = 2007 Academy Awards Nominations and Winner for Best Picture | work = [[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] | publisher = IMDb | accessdate = 2016-01-29}}</ref>。

提名公布时，获最佳影片奖提名的5部电影都没有登上2007年[[美国电影|美国电影]]票房10强榜。其中《朱诺》以8709万2615美元居首<ref name="EW" />，其后分别是收入4889万9543美元的《老无所依》，进账3939万9327美元的《迈克尔·克莱顿》，收入3265万3183美元的《赎罪》和进账869万6622美元的《血色将至》<ref name="BoxOfficeMojoOscars" />。

在1987年[[美国电影|美国电影]]票房50强中，有12部电影获得共计29项提名。其中《美食总动员》（第9名）、《美国黑帮》（第18名）、《朱诺》（第31名）、《查理·威尔森的战争》（第39名）和《冲浪企鹅》（第41名）所获提名包含最佳影片、动画长片、导演或编剧、表演类奖项。<ref name="boxofficemojooscars50">{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151223091224/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?asof=2008-01-21&view=releasedate&view2=domestic&yr=2007&sort=gross&order=DESC&p=.htm | publisher = IMDb | accessdate = 2016-01-29 | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?asof=2008-01-21&view=releasedate&view2=domestic&yr=2007&sort=gross&order=DESC&p=.htm | title = 2007 Yearly Box Office Results (January 21, 2008) | work = Box Office Mojo | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-12-23}}</ref>另外7部获提名的电影分别是《变形金刚》（季军）、《加勒比海盗3：世界的尽头》（第4名）、《谍影重重3》（第7名）、《魔法奇缘》（第20名）、《诺比特》（第29名）、《黄金罗盘》（第37名）和《决斗犹马镇》（第45名）<ref name="boxofficemojooscars50" />。

=== 专业评价 ===
本次颁奖典礼所获评价褒贬不一，部分媒体看法倾向负面。《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》电视评论员[[汤姆·谢尔斯|汤姆·谢尔斯]]（{{lang|en|Tom Shales}}）取笑晚会堆积了太多的电影片段，不但有本届提名作品，还有早在[[第1届奥斯卡金像奖|1929年]]时获奖的电影，整个节目看上去令人就像老在打嗝般难受<ref>{{cite news|last=Shales |first=Tom |title=Oscar Viewers Got Clipped, In More Ways Than One |accessdate=2016-01-29 |work=The Washington Post |publisher=The Washington Post Company |date=2008-02-25 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20140702123058/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2008/02/25/AR2008022500046.html |archivedate=2014-07-02 |deadurl=no |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2008/02/25/AR2008022500046.html }}</ref>。《[[时代_(杂志)|时代]]》周刊专栏作家詹姆斯·波尼沃兹克（{{lang|en|James Poniewozik}}）认为，斯图尔特的主持虽然偶尔还算有趣，但总体上还是过分偏向传统，所有的段子都很中规中矩、大打安全牌，要么是[[科林·法雷尔|科林·法雷尔]]怎么性感，[[凯特·布兰切特|凯特·布兰切特]]戏路如何宽泛，再不然就拿[[杰克·尼科尔森|杰克·尼科尔森]]开涮，说他是个老色鬼。对于节目本身，波尼沃兹克认为其中充斥的回顾片段太多，如果这时编剧还在罢工倒还合理，但实际情况并非如此。与此同时，晚会也过于沉闷乏味。<ref>{{cite news | last = Poniewozik | first = James | title = Oscars Defeat Jon Stewart | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151222155844/http://entertainment.time.com/2008/02/25/oscars_defeat_jon_stewart/ | url = http://entertainment.time.com/2008/02/25/oscars_defeat_jon_stewart/ | accessdate = 2016-01-29 | work = [[时代_(杂志)|Time]] | publisher = Time Warner | date = 2008-02-25 | archivedate = 2015-12-22 | deadurl = no}}</ref>《[[今日美国|今日美国]]》专栏作家罗伯特·比安科（{{lang|en|Robert Bianco}}）认为，正是编剧大罢工导致主办方只有几星期时间准备，令周日晚直播的奥斯卡颁奖显得非常无聊，大量内容都不得不依靠视频片段填补，节目本身乏善可陈。他还认为，大量的视频片段令斯图尔特作为主持人的作用显得可有可无。<ref>{{cite news | last = Bianco | first = Robert | title = The Latest Strike Casualty: This Show | work = USA Today | publisher = Gannett Company | date = 2008-02-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151113015539/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/movieawards/oscars/2008-02-25-bianco-review_N.htm | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/movieawards/oscars/2008-02-25-bianco-review_N.htm | accessdate = 2016-01-29 | archivedate = 2015-11-13 | deadurl = no}}</ref>

其他大部分媒体对节目有更加正面的评价。《[[波士顿环球报|波士顿环球报]]》（{{lang|en|''Boston Globe''}}）电视评论员马修·吉尔伯特（{{lang|en|Matthew Gilbert}}）觉得晚会总体表现一般，但斯图尔特主持功底不凡。评论中称：“很高兴看到乔恩·斯图尔特的本色演出。他已在[[比利·克里斯托|比利·克里斯托]]离开后成长为值得信赖的奥斯卡主持。虽然在音乐上并不擅长，但他依然多才多艺，足以在取笑政治、好莱坞、新媒体，以及取笑发型这最压轴的笑点上自由穿棱，游刃有余。”<ref>{{cite news | last = Gilbert | first = Matthew | title = Looking back doesn't help show look good | accessdate = 2016-01-29 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.boston.com/ae/movies/oscars/articles/2008/02/25/looking_back_doesnt_help_show_look_good/ | work = The Boston Globe | publisher = John W. Henry | date = 2008-02-25 | archivedate = 2015-05-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150503135954/http://www.boston.com/ae/movies/oscars/articles/2008/02/25/looking_back_doesnt_help_show_look_good/}}</ref>《[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]]》杂志专栏作家布莱恩·洛瑞（{{lang|en|Brian Lowry}}）同样称赞主持人的表现，称他无论是在取笑凯特·布兰切特的宽广戏路，还是在{{lang|en|[[iPhone|iPhone]]}}的小屏幕上观看《[[阿拉伯的劳伦斯_(电影)|阿拉伯的劳伦斯]]》时都保持着一种俏皮、揶揄的风格<ref name="Variety Oscar" />。[[美联社|美联社]]评论员弗雷泽·摩尔（{{lang|en|Frazier Moore}}）认为，斯图尔特的表现比起上次主持已有明显改善，虽然前期准备时间非常紧，晚会现场节奏也很快，但事实证明他完全能够胜任，甚至就像在自己家里一样轻松自如。摩尔还觉得，虽然各奖项结果缺乏惊喜，但这个夜晚仍然非常优雅，舞台设计高档大气，管弦尔雄浑而又生机盎然，每个人都表现出自己最好的一面<ref>{{cite news | last = Moore | first = Frazier | title = The writers were back for the Oscarcast, but this show was nothing to write home about | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1673&dat=20080225&id=nrIjAAAAIBAJ&sjid=WSQEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6788,6000417&hl=en | accessdate = 2016-01-29 | work = The Press Democrat | publisher = Sonoma Media Investments LLC | date = 2008-02-25 | archive-date = 2016-03-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160308012343/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1673&dat=20080225&id=nrIjAAAAIBAJ&sjid=WSQEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6788,6000417&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

=== 收视率和奖项 ===
本届颁奖典礼通过美国广播公司在美国直播，其播出时段里平均有3200万观众收看，与[[第79届奥斯卡金像奖|前一年]]相比降低了21%<ref name="JoalRyan_2005_02_25" />，所有曾观看部分时段节目的观众总数则估计有6400万<ref>{{cite news|last=De Moraes |first=Lisa |title=Box-Office Blues Make for an Oscar Washout |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20140702123039/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2008/02/25/AR2008022501326.html |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2008/02/25/AR2008022501326.html |accessdate=2016-01-29 |work=[[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]] |publisher=The Washington Post Company |deadurl=no |date=2008-02-26 |archivedate=2014-07-02 }}</ref>。从尼尔森收视率调查数据来看，节目表现也不及前一年，吸引到18.7%的家庭观看，收视率为29%<ref>{{cite news | last = Bialik | first = Carl | title = And the Oscar Goes to… Fewer TV Viewers | url = http://blogs.wsj.com/numbers/and-the-oscar-goes-to-fewer-tv-viewers-283/ | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151225043745/http://blogs.wsj.com/numbers/and-the-oscar-goes-to-fewer-tv-viewers-283/ | date = 2008-02-26 | accessdate = 2016-01-29 | work = The Wall Street Journal | publisher = News Corp | archivedate = 2015-12-25}}</ref>。此外，节目在18至49岁年龄段观众群中收获的收视率为10.7 / 26，这意味着全美所有18至49岁年龄段人群里有10.7%观看颁奖典礼，而当时有看电视的该年龄段观众群中则有33.71%选择收看该节目<ref>{{cite news | last = Kissell | first = Rick | title = ‘Idol’ wins over Oscar in ratings | publisher = Penske Media Corporation | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151223071629/http://variety.com/2008/scene/features/idol-wins-over-oscar-in-ratings-1117981494/ | url = http://variety.com/2008/scene/features/idol-wins-over-oscar-in-ratings-1117981494/ | accessdate = 2016-01-29 | work = Variety | date = 2008-02-26 | archivedate = 2015-12-23 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。多家媒体认为，编剧协会的大罢工和提名电影相对小众共同影响，导致晚会收视率偏低<ref>{{cite news | last = Collins | first = Scott | title = TV ratings hit new low | url = http://articles.latimes.com/2008/feb/26/entertainment/et-oscarratings26 | accessdate = 2016-01-29 | work = Los Angeles Times | publisher = Tribune Company | date = 2008-02-26 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151222135904/http://articles.latimes.com/2008/feb/26/entertainment/et-oscarratings26 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-12-22}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Smith | first = Sean | title = Oscar's dropping ratings | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151129103303/http://www.ew.com/article/2008/02/29/oscars-dropping-ratings | url = http://www.ew.com/article/2008/02/29/oscars-dropping-ratings | accessdate = 2016-01-29 | work = [[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]] | publisher = Time Inc. | date = 2008-02-29 | archivedate = 2015-11-29 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。奥斯卡颁奖典礼是从1974年的[[第46届奥斯卡金像奖|第46届]]开始统计收视观众人数，截至[[第87届奥斯卡金像奖|2015年]]，第80届颁奖典礼的收视人数仍然垫底<ref name="Finke" />。

2008年7月，颁奖典礼获得[[第60届黄金时段艾美奖|第60届]][[黄金时段艾美奖|黄金时段艾美奖]]的9项提名<ref>{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151223092732/http://www.emmys.com/shows/80th-annual-academy-awards | deadurl = no | title = Primetime Emmy Award database | url = http://www.emmys.com/shows/80th-annual-academy-awards | accessdate = 2016-01-29 | publisher = Academy of Television Arts and Sciences (ATAS) | archivedate = 2015-12-23}}</ref>，并在两个月后赢得综艺、音乐或喜剧节目类杰出艺术指导和杰出导演奖<ref>{{cite news | title = 2008 Emmy winners | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151111072256/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/television/televisionawards/emmys/2008-09-21-emmy-winner-list_N.htm | accessdate = 2016-01-29 | work = USA Today | publisher = Gannett Company | deadurl = no | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/television/televisionawards/emmys/2008-09-21-emmy-winner-list_N.htm | archivedate = 2015-11-11 | date = 2008-09-21}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Sepinwall | first = Alan | title = Sepinwall on TV: Recapping the Emmys | url = http://www.nj.com/entertainment/tv/index.ssf/2008/09/sepinwall_on_tv_recapping_the.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151223111211/http://www.nj.com/entertainment/tv/index.ssf/2008/09/sepinwall_on_tv_recapping_the.html | accessdate = 2016-01-29 | work = The Star-Ledger | publisher = Advance Publications | date = 2008-09-21 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-12-23}}</ref>。

